name: Brooklyn: 2nd Street (South) - Keap Street

South 2nd Street, at the southwest corner of Keap Street. Shown is the modern addition to Public School No. 19 at the northwest corner of South 3rd and Keap Street. The old building is on the right, at South 2nd Street.
